  <brief_title>The Effect of Lidocaine Patch for Postoperative Pain</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Efficacy and Safety of 5% Lidocaine Patch for Postoperative Pain in Unilateral Inguinal Herniorrhaphy</official_title>
